WEATHER SUMMARY:
LOW 998 HPA S OF ICELAND IS MOV SLWY E AND FLN. IN CONNECTION WITH THE
LOW UNSTABLE AIR WITH SHWRS OVER THE FAROES. ANOTHER LOW 1000 HPA W OF SCOTLAND
IS MOV NE AND N TOWARDS THE EASTERN WATERS WITH SOME RAIN.
